title: Top #SUNtravelpics reader photos from July 2015 [Photos]
text:
Friday, July 31, 2015 08:44 AM EDT Top #SUNtravelpics reader photos from July 2015 
Long Beach on Lake Erie by Terry Langlois. Theme: Canada's beaches (July 9) 
Sunset off Lake Huron shores at St. Joseph, Ontario by Barb Peterson. Theme: Canada's beaches (July 9) 
Wasaga Beach, Ontario by Jack Milczynski. Theme: Canada's beaches (July 9) 
Ontario parks rock! By Laura Gazley via Twitter. Theme: Camping (July 16, 2015) 
The big Lobster at Shediac, New Brunswick. We look for the big road side attractions across Canada and then camp nearby to learn more about the community and the importance of these 'Big things'. By George Finch, Exeter, Ont. Theme: Camping (July 16, 2015) 
Wesley campground, Kanata, Ont. My son Hunter and I. By Rene Ressler, St. Catharines, Ont. Theme: Camping (July 16, 2015) 
Gorgeous day coming out of Port Dalhousie last year when the pier was still open by Stephanie Goertz. Theme: The lake (July 23, 2015) 
Port Albert, Ontario - Louch family week at the cottage by Scott Louch. Theme: The lake (July 23, 2015) 
I took this photo on July 10, 2015 on Lake Moira at Madoc, Ont. by Gwen Swart. Theme: The lake (July 23, 2015) 
Jumping off the Pier into Lake Huron, Kincardine, Ont. by Dave Cook. Theme: The lake (July 23, 2015) 
Pennsylvania by swall88. Theme: Rainbows (July 30, 2015) 
Sosua, Dominican Republic by Franz Hasenhundl. Theme: Rainbows (July 30, 2015) 
This photo was taken from the Rocky Mountaineer train last September. By Lorraine Ward. Theme: Rainbows (July 30, 2015) 
Sedona, Arizona by Joanne Foster. Theme: Rainbows (July 30, 2015)
